content: Here are the details for the productions I've seen: March 25th - "Rent" at the city theater, April 2nd - "The Storyteller" at a small fringe theater, April 10th - dress rehearsal for a play I worked on as a stagehand (can't wait to see it from the audience's perspective!), April 17th - attended the opening night of the same play, and April 22nd - "The Importance of Being Earnest" at a university theater.
